---
title: Crispy Chicken with Brown-Butter Corn and Cucumber Tomato Salad
description: Fried chicken is the ultimate comfort food. The only problem? It often comes with a side of guilt. Our chefs, Freida and Nate, found a way around this by coating  chicken thighs with panko and sour cream. The combination of this richly flavored cut of meat and ridiculously easy breading produces the enviable crispiness of the Southern chicken dish without the actual frying.
